I picked all these. Even the names.
- Oh really?

34
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,080
Hamasaki, Iku.

35
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:05,760
This girl's the main character.

36
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,540
"Iku" as in to live.
- Yes, Iku as in to live.

37
00:02:08,540 --> 00:02:11,240
Later there'll be an explanation as to why.

38
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:14,980
And Hamasaki Masayuki [Hamada Masatoshi]

39
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,220
Iku's father.

40
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:19,680
And the Principal is Matsumoto Hitoshi.

41
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:22,020
The Teacher role is Tanaka.

42
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:24,420
And the PE teacher is Endo.

43
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,900
However, it's all the "Iku" character.

44
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,540
For me, that sticks out.

45
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:33,280
Yeah, now that you mention it.

46
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:38,840
Yea, you're right! I could've written "Vice Principal" or something.

47
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:44,160
