- That's true!

48
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,800
Mm, I really apologize for that.

49
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:48,140
You could've even flipped these, I feel.

50
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:50,480
Tanaka was on screen a lot.

51
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,360
