362
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:12,260
Yeah, that's true.

363
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:17,420
In Hamada's scene, Iku already knows you're behind the tree.

364
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,240
The tree's too far away.

365
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:23,200
The tree and Hamada are too far away.

366
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:26,940
There's no way he would've heard with the cicadas.

367
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,680
He did hear it.

368
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:32,620
What's with this guy?

369
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,740
What role is that?

370
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:37,740
He ain't even directing...

371
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:40,560
I don't get it.

372
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:43,300
Let's get started!

373
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,180
Alright! Here we go!

374
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:50,880
Big scene! Big scene!

375
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:53,500
I'm leaving at 5.

376
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:56,980
It doesn't matter, waiting is work too.

377
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:01,820
It's been a while tho.

378
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:05,240
Ready...and...start!

379
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,580
Thank you very much.

380
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:18,000
He was feelin it! He was feelin it!

381
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,680
Those were real tears!

382
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:23,860
Also Endo's scene...

383
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:26,300
the picking up of the signboard.

